r-passthrough-141204527.html">下一代混合现实耳机</a>即将上市，它就会随之而来。随着沉浸感在 AR 和 VR 游戏中变得越来越重要，如果触觉获得一些关注，请不要感到惊讶。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/assassins-creed-haptic-shirt-will-make-you-feel-exclusive-sensations-never-felt-before-160041375.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/assassins-creed-haptic-shirt-will-make-you-feel-exclusive-sensations-never-felt-before-160041375.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 0da27b4f-5e52-47b5-bb35-d203a165b5cd</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jul 2023 16:00:41 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689350442</ingested><modified> 2023-07-14T16:00:45+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1563" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/25246210-2255-11ee-adae-340e3ce546c2" width="2944"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1563" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/25246210-2255-11ee-adae-340e3ce546c2" width="2944"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[OWO]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[OWO Assassin's Creed Mirage haptic shirt]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[OWO Assassin's Creed Mirage haptic shirt]]></